{"tid":976191,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解日本女性對出軌咁寬容","createTime":"2019-01-10T08:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T06:14:40.000Z","uid":148761,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbf7994af063724057345de477063073e280890","tid":976191,"uid":148761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"同個日本同事傾計<br />\n佢話日本啲女性對另一半出軌好寬容<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大多數會隻眼開隻眼閉<br />\n特別係唔小心既情況下<br />\n即係飲醉酒同第二個扑左野既時候<br />\n日本女性會選擇原諒<br />\n然後隔離個台灣妹話台灣既女性一定唔會原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋覺得唔理解同不可思議<br />\n<br />\n我都成日聽講過日本仔十個有九個都出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟日本妹會原諒係真係因為愛定乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解可以原諒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過睇返連登發覺好多巴絲打對另一半出軌都好寬容<br />\n好多都想原諒再重新黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70412250fb88c6dd415c04528d484563890ee2b","tid":976191,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:32:25.000Z","msg":"大男人主意"},{"pid":"5ae6d2a3ea74eea8b75fe89b605c64e69d1dfd06","tid":976191,"uid":99700,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:37:45.000Z","msg":"因為日本女人係雞而且好尊重av女優"},{"pid":"5c349646aec51b100d6768c9e72c79852a654d81","tid":976191,"uid":20624,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:38:34.000Z","msg":"因為雙方都成日岀軌"},{"pid":"f954466ac5cfa58fd063b849e02a0d38a9861ea1","tid":976191,"uid":67353,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"日本女仔多數結婚後就全職<br />\n咩都靠晒個男人<br />\n如果玩到離婚 出黎做野收入又唔夠"},{"pid":"5993a1bb6471d34fa6feadcf8f577b842d57c75c","tid":976191,"uid":208722,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:41:32.000Z","msg":"所以連登班毒撚特別吹奏日本"},{"pid":"7b06806bfa6fdd747f51